TextSection.Contents: A rare inborn error of amino acid metabolism characterized by elevated blood phenylalanine and low levels or absence of phenylalanine hydroxylase enzyme. If not detected early or left untreated the disorder manifests with mild to severe mental disability.

Parent.Label: Amino acid or protein metabolism disease with epilepsy
